---
---
<section id="features" class="section container">
    <span class="editorial-header">Everything you need</span>
    <div class="bento">
        <div class="bento-card bento-large">
            <div class="swiss-badge">Instant Import</div>
            <h3 class="display-sm">Build decks at the speed of thought.</h3>
            <p class="body-md bento-desc">Don't spend hours formatting. Paste a raw list of text into Spaced, and it automatically splits every line into front and back flashcards instantly. Or add them one by one.</p>
            <div class="code-block">Mitochondria : Powerhouse of the cell
Nucleus : Contains DNA
Ribosome : Protein synthesis</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bento-card bento-small">
            <div class="feature-icon">⟳</div>
            <h3 class="feature-title">Study Your Way</h3>
            <p class="body-sm">Flip cards, type your answer for auto-checking, reverse the deck (answer → prompt), shuffle, or drill only your starred "hard" cards.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bento-card bento-small">
            <div class="feature-icon">📂</div>
            <h3 class="feature-title">Study Hubs</h3>
            <p class="body-sm">A deck isn't just cards. Turn any topic into a study hub by attaching notes, links, files, and images directly alongside the flashcards.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bento-card bento-small">
            <div class="feature-icon">⏱</div>
            <h3 class="feature-title">Pomodoro + Active Recall</h3>
            <p class="body-sm">Focus Sessions work like a Pomodoro timer, keeping you locked in. But instead of just taking a break, the session ends with an active recall prompt to immediately solidify what you just learned.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bento-card bento-small">
            <div class="feature-icon">🔔</div>
            <h3 class="feature-title">Smart Reminders</h3>
            <p class="body-sm">Get a local notification the exact day a topic is due for review. All scheduled locally on your device without any servers.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .bento-desc { margin: 16px 0 32px; }

    .feature-icon {
        font-size: 28px;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        line-height: 1;
    }

    .feature-title {
        font-family: var(--font-mono);
        text-transform: uppercase;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        color: var(--ink);
        margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .code-block {
        background: var(--surface-card);
        border: 1px solid var(--hairline);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 16px;
        font-family: monospace;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: var(--muted);
        white-space: pre-wrap;
        overflow-wrap: break-word;
    }
</style>
